\c 99
\s Jehovha mutsvene ngaarumbidzwe
\p
\v 1 Jehovha anobata ushe; vanhu ngavabvunde; iye agere pakati pamakerubhi; nyika ngaizununguswe.
\v 2 Jehovha mukuru paZiyoni; ari kumusoro-soro kwavanhu vese.
\v 3 Ngavarumbidze zita renyu guru rinotyisa; ndiye Mutsvene.
\p
\v 4 Simba ramambo rinodawo kururamisa; imwi munosimbisa kururama, munotonga muchiruramisa pakati paJakove.
\v 5 Kudzai Jehovha Mwari wedu, munamate pachitsiko chetsoka dzake; ndiye Mutsvene.
\p
\v 6 Mozisi naAroni pakati pavapristi vake, naSamueri pakati pavanodana zita rake; vakadana kuna Jehovha, iye akavapindura.
\v 7 Akataura navo ari mushongwe yegore; vakachengeta zvipupuriro zvake nomutemo waakavapa.
\v 8 Makavapindura, Jehovha Mwari wedu; maiva Mwari aivakanganwira, kunyange makatsiva zvavaiita.
\p
\v 9 Kudzai Jehovha Mwari wedu, namatai pagomo rake dzvene; nokuti Jehovha Mwari wedu ndiye Mutsvene.
